value.0: Growing on the ground here is a simple, but beautiful flowering plant. It has brightly colored flowers of red and yellow. There is a very soft calming scent that permiates the air around the plant. Simply standing in its presence seems to melt the troubles of the world away, allowing you to relax no matter what your troubles may be.
